---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavBar from '../../components/NavBar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Legal Notice | ClaveON" description="Legal Notice ClaveON" lang="en" canonicalPath="/en/impressum">
  <NavBar lang="en" />
  <main class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 680px;">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Legal Notice</h1>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted);">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--text);">Information according to § 5 TMG</p>
          <p>Martin Lache<br />Liebigstraße 7<br />50823 Cologne, Germany</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--text);">Contact</p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@claveon.de" style="color: var(--blue);">info@claveon.de</a></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--text);">VAT</p>
          <p>Pursuant to § 19 UStG (German VAT Act), no VAT is charged (small business regulation). VAT is not shown separately on invoices.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--text);">Note</p>
          <p>This is a sole proprietorship without commercial registration. Information provided in reduced form in accordance with applicable law.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--text);">Dispute Resolution</p>
          <p>The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute resolution (ODR): <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--blue);">ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>. We are neither obligated nor willing to participate in dispute resolution proceedings before a consumer arbitration board.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
